        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-16",
        "text": "requirements were changed to allow multi-family condominium",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_mm": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0,
          "y_mm": -54
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-17",
        "text": "development, placing its continued existence in jeopardy. At this time a",
